   <pb facs="3"/>
   <head>To my Friend, the Author.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>TO praise Thee, is a Labour to no end;</l>
      <l>Since those, that read Thee, cannot but Commend.</l>
      <l>Let <hi>Envie</hi> read, and <hi>Envie</hi> will becom</l>
      <l>A <hi>Convert;</hi> or, at least, shee will be dum.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>G. S.</signed>
   </closer>
